    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>經典動作烹飪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投擲食物，在地圖上飛馳，與好友合作，準時為每位顧客服務。在限時遊戲模式中，挑戰不斷升級的關卡、工具和新食譜。每個關卡都與您的團隊規模相匹配，只有您的最高得分才有意義！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/02e70b508d40e6baea36ae24a4232d44.poster.avif?t=1750530198\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/02e70b508d40e6baea36ae24a4232d44.webm?t=1750530198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/02e70b508d40e6baea36ae24a4232d44.mp4?t=1750530198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多 4 人合作。關卡會根據團隊規模而變化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 個關卡，挑戰您的團隊合作或智慧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲內語音文字聊天</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過 20 種獨特的食譜，並可自行製作各種變體</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >海量帽子和配件等您解鎖！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超過 40 項成就</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/c0e7d978228caef29754c7adaa288a91.avif?t=1750530198\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>-------- 特殊模式 --------</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>無盡模式：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >從遊戲中的 3 個區域中選擇 1 個，進行無盡奔跑。使用可放置的裝備或為團隊提供額外獎勵來升級您的跑步。廚師，加班吧，因為我們有很多顧客要來！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/a37dffa09551c1565f6c1f8f7374c72b.poster.avif?t=1750530198\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/a37dffa09551c1565f6c1f8f7374c72b.webm?t=1750530198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/a37dffa09551c1565f6c1f8f7374c72b.mp4?t=1750530198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>食物大戰：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或許，從烹飪和與朋友的爭論中休息一下。是時候決定誰才是廚房裡的主廚了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/9e017aaa13de3cf515f4d77c2110ca80.poster.avif?t=1750530198\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/9e017aaa13de3cf515f4d77c2110ca80.webm?t=1750530198\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145460/extras/9e017aaa13de3cf515f4d77c2110ca80.mp4?t=1750530198\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >開發者筆記：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好，如果您讀到這裡，非常感謝。 《Foodslingers》首先是一款旨在帶來樂趣和獨特體驗的遊戲。無論是搗鼓搗鼓，或是完成所有關卡或成就。我一直希望創造能夠在朋友之間留下美好回憶的體驗。話雖如此，參與社群活動實際上會對遊戲的設計和體驗產生影響，或許還能將他們的名字和外觀銘刻在遊戲中。我在這裡就是為了與玩家們一起打造這種體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kenny (Tinfoil)</p>",
